<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5380995>
    dc:description "FIG. 25. Endymiomyia quadra (stem-group Bombyliidae?), new genus and species, holotype JZC Bu-209. A. Wing, dorsal view. B. Detail of wing base, dorsal view. C. Detail of anterior portion of head, ventral view. D. Face, with antennae and mouthparts, oblique frontal view. E. Detail of antenna, lateral view. F. Male terminalia, dorsal view. Panels E, F to same scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5380995/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5381061>
    dc:description "FIG. 57. Endymiomyia quadra, new genus and species (stem-group Bombyliidae), holotype JZC Bu-209. A. Habitus, dorsal view. B. Head and thorax, dorsal view. C. Base of abdomen, showing long lateral pilosity. D. Male terminalia, dorsal." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5381061/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

